('computer-science:2-2-3d-sql:match:47fe2eff', 'computer-science', 'computer-science:2-2-3d-sql', '2.2.3d SQL', 'match', 'mcq', 1, '{"question": "Which definition matches the key term “WHERE”?", "options": ["Filters which rows (records) are returned, based on a condition", "Checks whether a field''s value does NOT equal a given value", "Check whether a value is bigger / smaller than another, excluding an exact match", "Chooses which field(s) — columns — a query returns"]}'::jsonb, '{"answer": 0, "explain": "“WHERE” means: Filters which rows (records) are returned, based on a condition"}'::jsonb),
